Replacement
Given a string, a letter in the string and a random letter, replace all instances of the first letter with the latter.

Example
Input
Input String: Test me
Replace: e
Replace with: K

Output
TKst mK

# take in the number
n = int(input())

# calculate answer


# print answer
print(answer)

Solution:
# take in the number
text = input()
replace = input()
replaceWith = input ()

# calculate answer
answer = text.replace(replace, replaceWith)


# print answer
print(answer)
